* Major protocol upgrades

: softfork upgrades: restrict set of valid txns/blocks
: hardfork upgrade: expand set of valid txns/blocks

- P2SH: [[https://github.com/bitcoin/bips/blob/master/bip-0016.mediawiki][BIP16]]
:   add special-case validation to do an extra things when P2SH pattern is seen
:   when creating output, provide hash of a script
:   evaluation to pop embedded script and run it
- CSV/CLTV: [[https://github.com/bitcoin/bips/blob/master/bip-0065.mediawiki][BIP65]] / [[https://github.com/bitcoin/bips/blob/master/bip-0112.mediawiki][BIP112]]
: script to be restricted until certain time / age of output
: allows HTLCs, used in LN, as well as escrow, freezing funds and other contracts
- SegWit: [[https://github.com/bitcoin/bips/blob/master/bip-0141.mediawiki][BIP141]], [[https://github.com/bitcoin/bips/blob/master/bip-0143.mediawiki][BIP143]], [[https://github.com/bitcoin/bips/blob/master/bip-0144.mediawiki][BIP144]], [[https://github.com/bitcoin/bips/blob/master/bip-0145.mediawiki][BIP145]], [[https://github.com/bitcoin/bips/blob/master/bip-0147.mediawiki][BIP147]], [[https://github.com/bitcoin/bips/blob/master/bip-0173.mediawiki][BIP173]]
:   add special-case that if 0 [data] is on unlock script, data is
:   pubkey and signature, seen as anyone-can-spend by old nodes
:   capacity upgrade, fixes transaction malleability
:   also allows for versioning updates to script

* Major bugs (1/2)

